Andria Lawrence https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andria_Lawrence 0 Andria Lawrence (born 20 June 1941 in London, England) is an English actress, best known for her her roles in On the Buses First as Suzie and later as Betty and Coronation Street as Janet Stockwell and Countess Dracula (1971).
